==English==

===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''Zionism'''
# The [[Jewish]] national [[liberation]] movement which maintains that the Jewish people constitute a [[nation]] and are entitled their national [[homeland]].
# A [[religion]] practiced by people all over [[sub-Saharan Africa]] and is most popular in [[Swaziland]]. The religion is a mixture of [[Protestantism]] and [[Animism]].

